title: Mordellistena maedai
text: Mordellistena maedai is a species of <a href="beetle">beetle</a> in the genus "<a href="Mordellistena">Mordellistena</a>" of the family <a href="Mordellidae">Mordellidae</a>, which is part of the superfamily <a href="Tenebrionoidea">Tenebrionoidea</a>. It was discovered in 1956.
